sentences: The Gambia, on behalf of the AFRICAN GROUP, supported by ALGERIA, EGYPT, BOLIVIA and VENEZUELA called for all contact groups under the AWG-KP to be suspended until conclusion of work by the contact group on Annex I emission reductions.
The EU expressed regret with the African Group s proposal, highlighting that it is not realistic for one contact group to work faster than another.
Co-Chair Ure suspended the meeting until further notice.
